project_descr: Sustainable Forest landscape management in the Central Forest Spine to secure critical wildlife habitats, conserve biodiversity and carbon stokcs and maintain the continous flow of multiple ecosystems services.

outputs.output_descr: This project will conserve biodiversity and ecosystem services in three critical landscapes of the Central Forest Spine, by supporting the country’s CFS Master Plan to restore connectivity between forest complexes.

project_title: improving connectivity in central forest spine
